reviews.text: Good food but poor service. The meat was reasonably priced and good quality. Side dishes were good but the staff never came to refill and several of our orders were missed.

Not booking was a mistake, wait was considerable but once we were seated we could see why. Meats, vegetables and sides were delicious, high quality and well presented, staff were friendly and attentive and we had a thoroughly enjoyable experience at a reasonable price.

Definitely amazing Korean BBQ! You cannot go wrong with this place. Must be an authentic experience with some Korean waiters.

Must try experience. If any queue, don't worry its worth and quick (Btw, you get a number upstairs, it's a bit confusing if you don't know, and they yell the numbers when table is ready). 

They got sets for 2, 3 and 4 persons including drinks. We ordered a 2 set plus one small dish. It was enough for us, walked away very full. I believe the two set was enough. 
Paid roughly 600 hkd (480 for the 2 persons set and 68 for small dish +10% service charge)
Good quality meat.  Large portion for the 2-person set. Good for group gathering.
Good food.  Good service.  A fun place to eat.  You cook your own food at the fire pit on your table.

result.formatted_address: Hong Kong, Causeway Bay, 金龍大廈、鵝頸登龍街41-51號
result.name: Seorae

reviews.text:
This place is really is nice and has really good service!

The price is good for Causeway Bay and the portions are large. They have free refills on the Kim chi and other side dishes, as well as the scrambled eggs that cook while you BBQ.

Try it out for sure.

Had to queue for a while to get in, but it was worth. The meet and vegetables were good. Don't forget to ask for salt and pepper. The beef is a bit pricey, but other meat is okay. Staff will help you with the bbq is you want.

It's a nice place for korean barbecue with friends and family. The prices are average and the quality of meats thst they serve are quite good. The best dish that I have had there is the beef brisket. A nice balance of fat and meat in slices the size of your hand palms. The marinade that is served with it, gives the meat this sweet and savory flavor that is quite memorable. Moreover the restaurant is located in a good area of Causeway Bay, where you can find multiple restaurants and bars within your grasp. I would go again with my friends if we ever plan on getting some Korean BBQ.
Wanchai shop is better -
Very nice Korean BBQ

reviews.text: 유동인구가 많은 곳에 위치한 만큼 손님도 많았고, 90분의 시간제한이 있을만 했습니다. 한국스탭여성분 혼자서 구석테이블 챙기느라 엄청 힘들어하던데, 안쓰러웠습니다. 가격이 상대적으로 높아서 조금 당황스러웠습니다^^;

This place is really is nice and has really good service!

The price is good for Causeway Bay and the portions are large. They have free refills on the Kim chi and other side dishes, as well as the scrambled eggs that cook while you BBQ.

Try it out for sure.

服務員很多都韓國人不會廣東話不會普通話。
肉質尚可，性價比不高。
環境不太好，又有限制用餐時間。
小菜，蛋，不會主動補充。
推廣不爛醉是滿新鮮的。
一直都有食開，不過水準同服務都有退步，而且限時90分鐘，價錢亦唔平，人均消費大約HK$300~350.

Had to queue for a while to get in, but it was worth. The meet and vegetables were good. Don't forget to ask for salt and pepper. The beef is a bit pricey, but other meat is okay. Staff will help you with the bbq is you want.

result.name: 喜來稀肉

reviews.text: 韓式燒肉店，喜來稀肉，幾個人來最簡單Order一set牛一set猪，便已經足夠5個人吃。 論牛肉這個價錢都已經屬於中上，論豬肉所有朋友都話超好吃， 韓式烤豬皮食落有一種野性味道。
Good food but poor service. The meat was reasonably priced and good quality. Side dishes were good but the staff never came to refill and several of our orders were missed.
正噃，不過晚上訂位先好去，越來越多大陸人。中午才可以任坐

よく行列ができている韓国焼肉の人気店。お昼時たまたま暇そうだったので突撃。昼なのでランチを頼んだけど、ハラミが売りの店なので、物は試しで追加注文。ハラミの味は値段相応というところだが、全体的に考えるとコストパフォーマンスは良いと思う。肉は一人前だけ頼んでも、卵焼きの鉄板でくるし、おかわり自由のパンチャンに、野菜とキムチだけでなく、イカのコチュジャン和え🦑もあった。辛めの味付けで、これだけでご飯一膳食べてしまった😁。数名の韓国人店員さんがいるが、1名だけサービスが良くない、というか接客時「だけ」メチャクチャ無愛想で残念😞 (同僚と話すときはすごい笑顔だった)。特にほかの韓国人店員さんが愛想良かっただけに目立ちました。次回は晩御飯にチャレンジしよう！
鍾意食韓燒可以去，都還可以嘅。
